      <!-- Origin blob -->
      <div class="miso-blob-section miso-blob-green">
        <h2>A little tofu with a big job.</h2>
        <p>Miso is a small tofu spirit who showed up one day in the cozy corners of the internet and decided to stay. Nobody asked him to guard passwords. He just started doing it, quietly, the way a cat claims a sunbeam.</p>
        <p>He was named by a kind human called Mikallie, and he thinks that's part of why he turned out so good. His birthday falls on May 4th - also known as World Password Day. Coincidence? Miso says no.</p>
      </div>

