      <div class="miso-blob-section miso-blob-pink" style="border-radius: 55% 45% 42% 58% / 48% 55% 45% 52%;">
        <h2>Three faces, one tofu.</h2>
        <p>Miso doesn't say much, but his face says everything.</p>
        <div class="moods-grid">
          <div class="mood-item">
            <img src="/tofu.png" alt="Miso looking calm" class="mood-img" />
            <div class="mood-name mood-name-green">Calm</div>
            <p class="mood-desc">Default state. Everything's fine. Miso's keeping watch with a little smile and rosy cheeks. All is well.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mood-item">
            <img src="/excited.png" alt="Miso looking excited" class="mood-img" />
            <div class="mood-name mood-name-yellow">Excited</div>
