          </div>
          <div class="mood-item">
            <img src="/alert.png" alt="Miso looking alert" class="mood-img" />
            <div class="mood-name mood-name-pink">Alert</div>
            <p class="mood-desc">Something needs attention. Maybe a policy update, maybe you're spam-clicking generate. The exclamation mark appears. Miso is concerned.</p>
