      <!-- Personality blob -->
      <div class="miso-blob-section miso-blob-yellow" style="border-radius: 45% 55% 58% 42% / 52% 48% 50% 50%;">
        <h2>Soft in personality, firm in protection.</h2>
        <p>Miso believes security should feel warm and easy to understand. He's not loud. He's not flashy. He just quietly makes sure things stay protected while you go about your day.</p>
        <p>He's the kind of friend who remembers your preferences but never shares them with anyone. Which is exactly what a password guardian should be.</p>
        <div class="fun-facts">
          <div class="fun-fact"><span class="fun-fact-label">Color</span><span class="fun-fact-value">Moss green</span></div>
          <div class="fun-fact"><span class="fun-fact-label">Snack</span><span class="fun-fact-value">Toasted sesame seeds</span></div>
          <div class="fun-fact"><span class="fun-fact-label">Hobby</span><span class="fun-fact-value">Collecting safe words</span></div>
          <div class="fun-fact"><span class="fun-fact-label">Fear</span><span class="fun-fact-value">Weak passwords & hot soup</span></div>
          <div class="fun-fact"><span class="fun-fact-label">Dream</span><span class="fun-fact-value">Zero sticky-note passwords</span></div>
          <div class="fun-fact"><span class="fun-fact-label">Song</span><span class="fun-fact-value">Marconi Union - Weightless</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Letter blob -->
      <div class="miso-blob-section miso-blob-purple" style="border-radius: 50% 50% 45% 55% / 55% 45% 52% 48%;">
