        <div class="miso-letter">
          <div class="miso-letter-stamp">Miso Post</div>
          <div class="miso-letter-body">
            <p>Hi friend,</p>
            <p>I know passwords can feel overwhelming. Lots of rules, lots of warnings, lots of "don't do this."</p>
            <p>But it doesn't have to be that way. A good random password and a safe place to keep it - that's really all you need.</p>
            <p>I'll be here whenever you need me. Quietly keeping watch, like always.</p>
            <p>Stay safe, stay cozy,</p>
            <p class="miso-letter-sign">Miso</p>
